<button [disabled]="disabled || !enabled"
        [ngClass]="{'hidden': visible != true}"
				[style.color]="fontColor"
				[id]="id"
				type="button" class="btn btn-default {{cssClass}}"
				(mousedown)="onMouseDown($event)"
				(click)="onClick($event)"
        (contextmenu)="handleOnContextMenu($event)"
        (blur)="handleOnBlur()"
        [ngStyle]="styles"
        [style.padding]="controlPadding"
        [style.margin-top]="marginTop"
        [style.margin-left]="marginLeft"
        [style.margin-right]="marginRight"
        [style.margin-bottom]="marginBottom"
        [style.line-height]="lineHeight">
	{{ text }}
	<!-- allow children (in case user want to display html) -->
	<ng-content></ng-content>
</button>

<textarea #textarea [id]="id" class="vt-text-area form-control {{cssClass}}"
[attr.disabled]="enabled !== false ? null : true"
  [attr.readonly]="editable !== false ? null : true"
  [style.height]="controlHeight"
  [style.maxWidth]="controlWidth"
  [style.padding]="controlPadding"
  [style.line-height]="lineHeight"
  [ngClass]="{'hidden': visible != true}"
  (focusin)="onFocus($event)"
  (focusout)="onBlur($event, textarea.value)"
  (keyup)="onInput($event, textarea.value)"
  (contextmenu)="handleOnContextMenu($event)"
  [ngStyle]="styles"
  [required]="required"
  [maxLength]="maxLength"
  [(ngModel)]="text"
  [disabled]="disabled"
  >
</textarea>
